- cs.ETR (Emerging Technologies) is a possibility as reversible logic has applications in low-energy computation and quantum computation, which are emerging technologies. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper may involve analysis of the complexity of the decomposition algorithm. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper may involve implementation of the decomposition algorithm.
